  "screens": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "刚才我们一直在说“算法交易”。",
        "那它到底是什么？"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "先别急着背定义。",
        "先看它到底做了哪两件事。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "第一件事，",
        "**<term id=\"decision_making\">决策</term>**。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "decision_making"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "decision_making"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "也就是：",
        "现在该买，还是该卖？"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "第二件事，",
        "**<term id=\"execution\">执行</term>**。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "execution"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "execution"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "也就是：",
        "这个判断要怎样真正下到市场里。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "先停一下。",
        "下面哪一句更像“执行”？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "选一个最接近执行环节的描述。",
        "options": [
          "判断趋势要不要做多",
          "把买入信号变成真实订单",
          "阅读公司新闻"
        ],
        "answer": 1,
        "explanation": "执行关心的是订单如何进入市场，不是信号如何产生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "所以 **<term id=\"algorithmic_trading\">算法交易</term>**，",
        "不是只有“想法”。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "algorithmic_trading"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "algorithmic_trading"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "它要把“怎么判断”，",
        "和“怎么执行”，都交给规则与程序。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "你还会看到几个近义叫法：",
        "Algo Trading、Quant Trading、Robo-Trading。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "先把它们看成同一家族。",
        "重点不是名字，而是流程是否被程序化。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "现在压缩成一句话。",
        "算法交易最少要同时碰到哪两块？"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "fill_in_blank",
        "prompt": "算法交易至少涉及 **____** 这两个环节。",
        "answers": [
          "决策和执行"
        ],
        "explanation": "一个负责形成信号，一个负责落地执行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "那它追求的是什么？",
        "只有赚钱吗？"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "不是。",
        "通常会同时盯住三个目标。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "第一，**<term id=\"maximize_profits\">提高收益</term>**。",
        "也就是尽量让策略赚得更多。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "maximize_profits"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "maximize_profits"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "第二，**<term id=\"control_execution_costs\">控制执行成本</term>**。",
        "也就是别在下单和成交时白白多付成本。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "control_execution_costs"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "control_execution_costs"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "第三，**<term id=\"hedging_and_risk_management\">对冲与风险管理</term>**。",
        "也就是在追求收益时，也要管住风险。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "hedging_and_risk_management"
      ],
      "introduced_terms": [
        "hedging_and_risk_management"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "type": "exercise",
      "lines": [
        "这里很关键。",
        "算法交易不是只盯着利润。"
      ],
      "exercise": {
        "kind": "single_choice",
        "prompt": "下面哪一个不属于刚才提到的目标？",
        "options": [
          "提高收益",
          "控制执行成本",
          "保证每次都赚钱"
        ],
        "answer": 2,
        "explanation": "材料强调收益、成本和风险管理，但从没承诺稳赚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "所以更完整的理解是：",
        "算法交易在设计一个可重复的交易流程。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这个流程既要能想，",
        "也要能做。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "既要争取收益，",
        "也要管住成本和风险。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "type": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "把这句话记住就够了：",
        "**<term id=\"algorithmic_trading\">算法交易</term>** 不是一个按钮，而是一条流程。"
      ],
      "focus_terms": [
        "algorithmic_trading"
      ]
    }
  ],
